# Generated shader pipelines: packed from assets/shadercode by the
# shader-pipelines target and converted to .pln by game-assets. (diffuse.txt and
# diffuse_vertex_color.txt are hand-authored pre-migration and stay committed;
# the binary .pln are covered by *.pln above.)
game/shaders/*.txt
game/**/*.png
# Engine-level fallback textures, committed (loaded unconditionally at startup).
!game/textures/default.png
!game/textures/flat_normal.png
*~

